rows.label: qst100202_msg0001
rows.name:
Ah ya ya...
Please calm down, friends.
Wait just few minutes more...

rows.label: qst100202_msg0003
rows.name:
If you don't back down I'll show you
the strength of Superbia!

rows.label: qst100202_msg0004
rows.name:
You lot won't be so strong when
your Divine Beast drags you all down into
the Cloud Sea!

rows.label: qst100202_msg0005
rows.name:
Oh go bang some rocks together
you primitive bumpkin!

rows.label: qst100202_msg0006
rows.name:
Ah ya ya...
They won't stop...
Help me, Drivers!

rows.label: qst100202_msg0009
rows.name: Try to rile them up more

rows.label: qst100202_msg0101
rows.name:
You expect me to back down after
he insults my homeland like that?

rows.label: qst100202_msg0102
rows.name:
Looks like I'm gonna have to give you
a practical lesson in military superiority!

rows.label: qst100202_msg0104
rows.name:
You both as bad as each other!
Please, Drivers must intervene!

rows.label: qst100202_msg0201
rows.name:
What was that, mate?
You after stealing this Delta Vessel
that I won fair and square?

rows.label: qst100202_msg0202
rows.name:
I'm not going to let you talk to me
like this!

rows.label: qst100202_msg0203
rows.name:
Agh, enough talk!
I'll gut you, you thieving Superbian,
and you lot with him!

rows.label: qst100202_msg0204
rows.name:
Good luck, friends!
Please do not die, thank you!
